    <article id="post-CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment" class="h-entry article article-type-post" itemprop="blogPost" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting">
  <div class="article-meta">
    <a href="/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/" class="article-date">
  <time class="dt-published" datetime="2021-06-09T01:09:54.000Z" itemprop="datePublished">2021-06-09</time>
</a>
    
  <div class="article-category">
    <a class="article-category-link" href="/cn/categories/05%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB/">05：如何选择坐标系?</a>
  </div>

  </div>
  <div class="article-inner">
    
    
      <header class="article-header">
        
  
    <h1 itemprop="name">
      <a class="p-name article-title" href="/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/">如何选择坐标系?</a>
    </h1>
  

      </header>
    
    <div class="e-content article-entry" itemprop="articleBody">
      
      
      	
      		<p>坐标系是GIS中最基本概念，其应用体现在人类活动的各个领域。从火箭发射、星际宇航，到工农业生产，再到城市导航、线路规划、个人定位，所有的活动都离不开坐标系统的支持，即使是您根本觉察不到他的存在。</p>
<p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs_adjustment_o1.jpg"></p>
<p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs_adjustment_o2.jpg"></p>
<p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs_adjustment_o5.jpg"></p>
<p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs_adjustment_o3.jpg"></p>
<p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs_adjustment_o7.jpg"></p>
<h3 id="1、坐标系是地图系统的基础"><a href="#1、坐标系是地图系统的基础" class="headerlink" title="1、坐标系是地图系统的基础"></a>1、坐标系是地图系统的基础</h3><p>坐标系提供了对空间数据的位置描述。一幅地图，无论简单还是复杂、无论数据量有多少，要显示，必须具备正确的坐标系统。</p>
<h3 id="2、坐标系概念、分类及定义示例"><a href="#2、坐标系概念、分类及定义示例" class="headerlink" title="2、坐标系概念、分类及定义示例"></a>2、坐标系概念、分类及定义示例</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs-adjust1.jpg"></p>
<h3 id="3、投影坐标系与地理坐标系的关系"><a href="#3、投影坐标系与地理坐标系的关系" class="headerlink" title="3、投影坐标系与地理坐标系的关系"></a>3、投影坐标系与地理坐标系的关系</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs-adjust2.jpg"></p>
<p>简单地说，投影坐标系统是地理坐标系通过正射投影而获得平面坐标系统，主要用于web端地图显示定义。</p>
<h3 id="4、坐标系统的几个关键概念"><a href="#4、坐标系统的几个关键概念" class="headerlink" title="4、坐标系统的几个关键概念"></a>4、坐标系统的几个关键概念</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs-adjust3.jpg"></p>
<h3 id="5、坐标系的选择原则"><a href="#5、坐标系的选择原则" class="headerlink" title="5、坐标系的选择原则"></a>5、坐标系的选择原则</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs-adjust4.jpg"></p>
<h3 id="6、投影类型的选择原则"><a href="#6、投影类型的选择原则" class="headerlink" title="6、投影类型的选择原则"></a>6、投影类型的选择原则</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs-adjust5.jpg"></p>
<h3 id="7、投影方式的确定方法"><a href="#7、投影方式的确定方法" class="headerlink" title="7、投影方式的确定方法"></a>7、投影方式的确定方法</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs-adjust6.jpg"></p>
<p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/cs-adjust7.jpg"></p>

      	
      
    </div>
    <footer class="article-footer">
      <a data-url="https://pyramidmap.github.io/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/" data-id="ckq3fxj2q00038gutc095fl39" data-title="如何选择坐标系?" class="article-share-link">分享</a>
      
      
        <a href="/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/#comments" class="article-comment-link">
          <span class="post-comments-count valine-comment-count" data-xid="/cn/2021/06/09/CS-transformation-and-XY-adjustment/" itemprop="commentCount"></span>
          留言
        </a>
      
      
  <ul class="article-tag-list" itemprop="keywords"><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/Javascript-API/" rel="tag">Javascript API</a></li><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/PyramidMap/" rel="tag">PyramidMap</a></li><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/Python-tools/" rel="tag">Python tools</a></li></ul>

    </footer>
  </div>
  
</article>




