    <article id="post-JS-Application-scenarios" class="h-entry article article-type-post" itemprop="blogPost" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting">
  <div class="article-meta">
    <a href="/cn/2021/04/13/JS-Application-scenarios/" class="article-date">
  <time class="dt-published" datetime="2021-04-13T05:53:18.000Z" itemprop="datePublished">2021-04-13</time>
</a>
    
  <div class="article-category">
    <a class="article-category-link" href="/cn/categories/PyramidMap-Javascript-API/">PyramidMap Javascript API</a>►<a class="article-category-link" href="/cn/categories/PyramidMap-Javascript-API/02%EF%BC%9A%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF/">02：应用场景</a>
  </div>

  </div>
  <div class="article-inner">
    
    
      <header class="article-header">
        
  
    <h1 itemprop="name">
      <a class="p-name article-title" href="/cn/2021/04/13/JS-Application-scenarios/">PyramidMap Javascript API 应用场景</a>
    </h1>
  

      </header>
    
    <div class="e-content article-entry" itemprop="articleBody">
      
      
      	
      		<p>PyramidMap Javascript API 面向web地图应用。面向应用层，必须考虑三个问题：Which map platform to development? which database to store?  Which framework running on?  我们称其为3W问题。PyramidMap在设计之初已经把上述问题的兼容纳入到技术范畴，目的就是通过核心组件模式实现异构地图平台、数据库和框架之间的敏捷适配以及与前端的低耦合甚至无关性。PyramidMap Javascript 套件可以最大程度降低对前端不同框架的整合难度。pyramidmap已提供对以下的兼容支持。</p>
<h3 id="1：Map平台"><a href="#1：Map平台" class="headerlink" title="1：Map平台"></a>1：Map平台</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/04/13/JS-Application-scenarios/mapplatform.png"></p>
<h3 id="2：地理数据库"><a href="#2：地理数据库" class="headerlink" title="2：地理数据库"></a>2：地理数据库</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/04/13/JS-Application-scenarios/database.png"></p>
<h3 id="3：前端框架"><a href="#3：前端框架" class="headerlink" title="3：前端框架"></a>3：前端框架</h3><p><img src="/cn/cn/2021/04/13/JS-Application-scenarios/framework.png"></p>

      	
      
    </div>
    <footer class="article-footer">
      <a data-url="https://pyramidmap.github.io/cn/2021/04/13/JS-Application-scenarios/" data-id="ckq3fxj2y00098gut1fbfculn" data-title="PyramidMap Javascript API 应用场景" class="article-share-link">分享</a>
      
      
        <a href="/cn/2021/04/13/JS-Application-scenarios/#comments" class="article-comment-link">
          <span class="post-comments-count valine-comment-count" data-xid="/cn/2021/04/13/JS-Application-scenarios/" itemprop="commentCount"></span>
          留言
        </a>
      
      
  <ul class="article-tag-list" itemprop="keywords"><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/Javascript-API%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF/" rel="tag">Javascript API应用场景</a></li><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/Web-GL/" rel="tag">Web GL</a></li><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/Web-JS/" rel="tag">Web JS</a></li></ul>

