    <article id="post-JS-QueryIdentify" class="h-entry article article-type-post" itemprop="blogPost" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting">
  <div class="article-meta">
    <a href="/cn/2021/04/13/JS-QueryIdentify/" class="article-date">
  <time class="dt-published" datetime="2021-04-13T05:53:18.000Z" itemprop="datePublished">2021-04-13</time>
</a>
    
  <div class="article-category">
    <a class="article-category-link" href="/cn/categories/PyramidMap-Javascript-API/">PyramidMap Javascript API</a>►<a class="article-category-link" href="/cn/categories/PyramidMap-Javascript-API/05%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2/">05：地图查询</a>
  </div>

  </div>
  <div class="article-inner">
    
    
      <header class="article-header">
        
  
    <h1 itemprop="name">
      <a class="p-name article-title" href="/cn/2021/04/13/JS-QueryIdentify/">PyramidMap Javascript API 地图查询</a>
    </h1>
  

      </header>
    
    <div class="e-content article-entry" itemprop="articleBody">
      
      
      	
      		<p>PyramidMap的地图查询功能，支持各种地图平台接口及其地图资源，例如ArcGIS及其online在线地图资源和本地托管的地图数据，GeoServer托管地图、Google Map、OSM、MapBox、天地图、高德/百度地图等在线资源。同时支持属性数据查询和空间地理位置查询，支持大数据量并发请求，无论是在线地图还是离线地图，都可以精准定位，并与用户自有的业务数据进行整合。可以根据用户服务器性能及网络负载情况，调整请求响应的返回值，确保地图展示的平滑稳定和数据的准确性。</p>
<h3 id="坐标系兼容及准确的定位"><a href="#坐标系兼容及准确的定位" class="headerlink" title="坐标系兼容及准确的定位"></a>坐标系兼容及准确的定位</h3><p>PyramidMap内部集成了对不同坐标系的转换及位置校准，包括GCS空间坐标系统和PCS投影坐标系统，并针对高德/百度等特殊的坐标定义，也进行了兼容处理，实现精准定位。</p>
<div id="dplayer1" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer1"),"autoplay":true,"loop":true,"video":{"url":"/cn/2021/04/13/JS-QueryIdentify/confirmLocation.b912eb77.mp4"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>

<h3 id="属性数据查询"><a href="#属性数据查询" class="headerlink" title="属性数据查询"></a>属性数据查询</h3><p>PyramidMap地图查询接口支持多数据源图层的属性查询，解析图层数据结构，支持多字段的联合查询，精准定位，并同步显示定位对象的详细信息。</p>
<div id="dplayer2" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer2"),"autoplay":true,"loop":true,"video":{"url":"/cn/2021/04/13/JS-QueryIdentify/mapSearch.5b2e5a25.mp4"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>

<h3 id="空间数据查询"><a href="#空间数据查询" class="headerlink" title="空间数据查询"></a>空间数据查询</h3><p>PyramidMap支持图层图形化空间数据查询。例如在城市管网地图上，可按照压力值及流向进行过滤查询，也可以按照城区或社区范围进行空间查询。</p>
<div id="dplayer3" class="dplayer hexo-tag-dplayer-mark" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><script>(function(){var player = new DPlayer({"container":document.getElementById("dplayer3"),"autoplay":true,"loop":true,"video":{"url":"/cn/2021/04/13/JS-QueryIdentify/userDefined.dd74c0e0.mp4"}});window.dplayers||(window.dplayers=[]);window.dplayers.push(player);})()</script>

      	
      
    </div>
    <footer class="article-footer">
      <a data-url="https://pyramidmap.github.io/cn/2021/04/13/JS-QueryIdentify/" data-id="ckq3fxj33000d8gutb4ic2056" data-title="PyramidMap Javascript API 地图查询" class="article-share-link">分享</a>
      
      
        <a href="/cn/2021/04/13/JS-QueryIdentify/#comments" class="article-comment-link">
          <span class="post-comments-count valine-comment-count" data-xid="/cn/2021/04/13/JS-QueryIdentify/" itemprop="commentCount"></span>
          留言
        </a>
      
      
  <ul class="article-tag-list" itemprop="keywords"><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/Web-GL/" rel="tag">Web GL</a></li><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/Web-JS/" rel="tag">Web JS</a></li><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2/" rel="tag">属性查询</a></li><li class="article-tag-list-item"><a class="article-tag-list-link" href="/cn/tags/%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2/" rel="tag">空间查询</a></li></ul>

    </footer>
  </div>
  
</article>




